# Assets - Fonts

This folder is for custom font files.

## Current Implementation

The website uses Google Fonts (loaded via CDN):
- **Poppins**: For headings - weights 400, 600, 700, 800
- **Inter**: For body text - weights 300, 400, 500, 600
- **Roboto Mono**: For prices - weights 400, 500

## Loading in HTML

Fonts are loaded in the `<head>` of each HTML file:
```html
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Roboto+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

## Custom Fonts

To add custom fonts:
1. Add font files (WOFF2, WOFF, TTF) to this folder
2. Use @font-face in CSS:
   ```css
   @font-face {
       font-family: 'MyCustomFont';
       src: url('fonts/mycustomfont.woff2') format('woff2');
       font-weight: 400;
       font-style: normal;
   }
